and let him sit on the horses.

1207
01:36:00,405 --> 01:36:01,805
He seemed to like it.

1208
01:36:02,541 --> 01:36:07,171
Hell, the first word he ever spoke
was "horsy," not "mama" or "dada."

1209
01:36:07,345 --> 01:36:08,506
Can you beat that?

1210
01:36:09,215 --> 01:36:12,672
One day a bee stung this old bay horse
right there on the butt...

1211
01:36:12,851 --> 01:36:14,649
...while Dale was sitting on him.

1212
01:36:14,819 --> 01:36:17,515
That old horse would have broke you
in two, but now Dale...

1213
01:36:17,689 --> 01:36:19,020
...he hung on.

1214
01:36:19,190 --> 01:36:22,126
That's the first time he ever smiled.

1215
01:36:25,230 --> 01:36:27,994
